# Storybook

Seven files per component: `Overview.mdx`, `Css.mdx`, `React.mdx`, `Element.mdx`, three `*.stories.tsx`, plus shared `fixtures.ts` and `snippets.ts`.

## Titles

- Stories: `{Category}/{Component}/{CSS|React|Web Components}` — use **"Web Components"**, not "Element"
- Overview: `<Meta title='{Category}/{Component}/Overview' name='Overview' />`

## Categories (README → sidebar)

| Roadmap | Storybook |
| ------- | --------- |
| Foundation | Foundations |
| Typography | Typography |
| Content | Content |
| Layout | Wrappers |
| Interaction | Actions |

## Overview MDX

- Import `FIGMA_LIBRARY_URL` from `../docs/links`
- Include "Choose an implementation" with links to all three layer docs
- Preview canvas from CSS stories

## storySort

Add the component under the correct category in `apps/storybook/.storybook/preview.tsx`.

Reference: `apps/storybook/src/button/` and `apps/storybook/src/link/Overview.mdx`
